      <para id="id15060576">Assignment 2</para>
      <list id="id10017446" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>The bookcase illustrated below needs reinforcement. Indicate where you would place a support/supports to strengthen the shelf.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id13399949">
        <figure id="id11835660">
          <media id="id11835660_media" alt="">
