      <list id="id5338344" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>The legs of a trestle that supports a tabletop are held in place by means of a length of rope. Will this structure be able to withstand forces of stress or compression? Explain your answer and suggest a solution for the problem.</item>
